    "description": "<strong>Welcome to E1L1.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/8fb2c9d499838ccc9327edf16f2c4c69.poster.avif?t=1645588124\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/8fb2c9d499838ccc9327edf16f2c4c69.webm?t=1645588124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/8fb2c9d499838ccc9327edf16f2c4c69.mp4?t=1645588124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A subterranean station located inside of an asteroid called E1L1, which is inside the Oort Cloud. One of the oldest known to man. Created by Jim Octothorpe, the 4th richest man, Octothorpe Consortium Aerosapce (OCA) has built E1L1 to begin investigation and mining of a mineral called, Uranium Monodex Fentanyl.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/adcbab4def62aa3913e1b2e822d1b122.poster.avif?t=1645588124\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/adcbab4def62aa3913e1b2e822d1b122.webm?t=1645588124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/adcbab4def62aa3913e1b2e822d1b122.mp4?t=1645588124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>OCA has hired, Philip Ackman, a middle aged Janitor to take care of the station when things get messy, and knowing how E1L1 is handled, everyone is a slob.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/7a0e1055445ca95ac23ec877a0657725.poster.avif?t=1645588124\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/7a0e1055445ca95ac23ec877a0657725.webm?t=1645588124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/7a0e1055445ca95ac23ec877a0657725.mp4?t=1645588124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In 2081, an unknown incident took place inside of the station, no one knows what happened or what happened to the scientist and workers in there. Philip Ackman is the station's only hope for recovery, can he do it?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/d952d0ffab2853981a6804f4dbaf0f4e.poster.avif?t=1645588124\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/d952d0ffab2853981a6804f4dbaf0f4e.webm?t=1645588124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898060/extras/d952d0ffab2853981a6804f4dbaf0f4e.mp4?t=1645588124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore a ruined space station where unknown horrors stalk every corner, every hallway, and every room. It's up to you, P. Ackman to find a way to rid E1L1 of it's horrors and make it out alive. Not only will you need your Rivet gun to survive, but you'll also need to monitor your oxygen and stamina while picking up various cards to unlock areas.",
